Description: The Patient Facts module, part of the larger SSDQA ecosystem, serves to assess the 
    availability of patient clinical data (in either an OMOP or PCORnet CDM format) by summarizing the 
    number of clinical events per year of follow-up for each patient in a cohort. These facts are 
    computed and stratified by visit type.
